My name is Emmanuel Chigozie Madubuike.

0:00:43.420,0:00:52.060
I'm from Anambra State, Nigeria.

0:00:52.060,0:00:57.480
The woman next to me is my lovely mum.

0:00:57.480,0:01:04.920
So, in 2013 I got the opportunity to travel to South Africa.

0:01:04.920,0:01:19.260
Before I travelled, one of my friends told me that he needed to take me somewhere

0:01:19.260,0:01:26.900
so that I could fortify myself spiritually to be strong.

0:01:26.900,0:01:32.300
This was for me to be wealthier than anyone in my family or my friends.

0:01:32.300,0:01:40.380
I liked the suggestion because I needed money.

0:01:40.380,0:01:43.960
I followed that person to a native doctor.

0:01:43.960,0:01:54.180
On the way, my friend told me that the person was a very strong native doctor and that he knew him.

0:01:54.180,0:01:55.460
I asked him if he had been going there.

0:01:55.460,0:01:59.380
He told me not to worry for he knew him.

0:01:59.380,0:02:07.040
We went there.

0:02:07.040,0:02:17.520
The man asked me my name and I told him and gave him my picture.

0:02:17.520,0:02:35.160
He told me that before anything, I should deposit 50,000 naira and I told him no problem.

0:02:35.160,0:02:39.700
I withdrew and gave him the money.

0:02:39.700,0:02:50.760
I told him that he should convince me that he knew what he was doing as a spiritualist.

0:02:50.760,0:03:10.900
I lost my father in 2011 and he told me that he was in Abuja having fun with some women.

0:03:10.900,0:03:29.640
I was wondering which father he was talking about and looked at my friend.

0:03:29.640,0:03:34.940
He tried to convince me by telling me that I am a great man

0:03:34.940,0:03:48.940
but I needed to hear something more vital and specific about me than that to convince me.

0:03:48.940,0:03:58.900
He did an incantation and after all, he still said the same thing concerning me

0:03:58.900,0:04:11.860
and he told me that as he was talking to me, my dad was in Abuja with a woman in a hotel.

0:04:11.860,0:04:20.020
I was wondering what hotel he was referring to when someone had passed away.

0:04:20.020,0:04:29.520
I didn’t want to tell him anything; I wanted to make a fool of him.

0:04:29.520,0:04:35.460
After that, I called my friend outside and told him that I was no longer interested

0:04:35.460,0:04:45.940
for this man told me that my dad was having fun when my dad had passed away many years ago.

0:04:45.940,0:04:52.840
I entered again and told the man that I wanted to talk to him.

0:04:52.840,0:04:56.400
I told him that I didn’t need him anymore and that I wanted my things – picture and money.

0:04:56.400,0:05:00.160
He said that I couldn’t take anything back.

0:05:00.160,0:05:11.420
I pointed to my money on his plate and he told me that I could not touch the money again.

0:05:11.420,0:05:18.120
I agreed but still asked him if I could take my picture and he gave it to me.

0:05:18.120,0:05:22.740
I thanked him and drove out.

0:05:22.740,0:05:27.660
I told that man that I was no longer interested and I would travel the way I was.

0:05:27.660,0:05:29.520
I knew I would make it.

0:05:29.520,0:05:41.360
The man suggested another man again and said that this very man was very strong.

0:05:41.360,0:05:51.580
If this man didn’t convince me, I should not give any money.

0:05:51.580,0:05:58.100
I made sure that I slept in the same room with that guy so that he would not call the native doctor

0:05:58.100,0:06:00.920
and be telling him about me.

0:06:00.920,0:06:06.020
At a point, I started thinking that they were trying to take my money.

0:06:06.020,0:06:11.800
I told him that we were going on the next day but both of us had to sleep in my house.

0:06:11.800,0:06:14.320
He accepted.

0:06:14.320,0:06:20.500
In the following morning, we went to a shrine.

0:06:20.500,0:06:31.160
Immediately we entered the place, the native doctor looked at me and called me by my name.

0:06:31.160,0:06:33.020
I was shocked.

0:06:33.020,0:06:36.580
He told me the reason why I was there.

0:06:36.580,0:06:38.340
I confirmed.

0:06:38.340,0:06:43.420
I told him that he was the man I was looking for.

0:06:43.420,0:06:52.840
He said to me that before everything, I had to pay 100,000.

0:06:52.840,0:06:56.640
I told him that 100,000 was not a problem and that I would provide.

0:06:56.640,0:07:01.980
I thought paying 100,000 to get millions was OK for me.

0:07:01.980,0:07:14.900
Then, we drove out to withdraw 100,000 and we came back to him.

0:07:14.900,0:07:25.200
There were some things they asked me to buy – goat, chicken – to fortify me.

0:07:25.200,0:07:26.020
I accepted it.

0:07:26.020,0:07:27.960
I went and bought the things with the money.

0:07:27.960,0:07:35.000
When we came back, I handed everything over to him.

0:07:35.000,0:07:43.140
Then, he asked me to kneel down in front of the shrine and I did.

0:07:43.140,0:07:53.140
He told me to say everything I needed in front of the oracle.

0:07:53.140,0:08:01.440
I knelt down and told the oracle that I needed fame, money and power.

0:08:01.440,0:08:04.920
I needed everything.

0:08:04.920,0:08:08.940
I wanted to be bigger than my friends.

0:08:08.940,0:08:12.360
He told me that it was done.

0:08:12.360,0:08:20.020
He said that he needed to give me one advice, as he knew that I was going to South Africa which I confirmed.

0:08:20.020,0:08:25.360
He said that it was very rough area where they shoot anyhow.

0:08:25.360,0:08:33.280
I needed to fortify myself against gun.

0:08:33.280,0:08:35.500
That was a good idea.

0:08:35.500,0:08:37.360
I asked if I had to bring more money.

0:08:37.360,0:08:41.840
He said that I should relax for now because it seemed that I was afraid to bring money.

0:08:41.840,0:08:51.380
I told him that I was not afraid but if he did a good job, bringing money was not a problem.

0:08:51.380,0:08:53.940
He started fortifying me.

0:08:53.940,0:08:57.360
He killed a chicken and we all ate it.

0:08:57.360,0:09:09.180
After we finished eating at the shrine, he put one chicken feather inside my boxer.

0:09:09.180,0:09:24.260
Then, he brought a little stone and a red cloth which he tore into two to wrap the stone.

0:09:24.260,0:09:31.500
After that, he brought water for me to swallow the stone.

0:09:31.500,0:09:53.060
Before giving it to me, he used to the stone for ritual.

0:09:53.060,0:10:00.300
I swallowed the stone and it entered my stomach.

0:10:00.300,0:10:02.860
I asked him, “What else?”

0:10:02.860,0:10:07.500
Immediately I swallowed it, instantly, I was not with myself;

0:10:07.500,0:10:13.520
it was as if another thing came upon me.

0:10:13.520,0:10:17.440
My body became heavy.

0:10:17.440,0:10:26.760
I told him that he was really doing something for me, he was really strong and that I liked him.

0:10:26.760,0:10:31.840
I told him that I felt strong.

0:10:31.840,0:10:39.900
He said that it was time to test what he had done for me by shooting me as he brought out his gun.

0:10:39.900,0:10:52.860
I told him that he could not shoot me.

0:10:52.860,0:10:57.720
He reminded me that I asked for power and he had fortified me and done everything.

0:10:57.720,0:11:02.180
So, he needed to test it.

0:11:02.180,0:11:09.460
When you take an exam, you need to show what you studied.

0:11:09.460,0:11:17.660
After doing everything for me, they had to test it.

0:11:17.660,0:11:23.960
I asked him what would happen if he didn’t do things well and the bullet entered me

0:11:23.960,0:11:29.440
and I would die without my family knowing where I was.

0:11:29.440,0:11:38.040
I told him that as a spiritual man, I believed the spirit didn’t show him things well.

0:11:38.040,0:11:39.980
I asked him to test it on another thing.

0:11:39.980,0:11:45.020
He agreed but at the end, he still had to test it on me.

0:11:45.020,0:11:58.140
He put the feather and stone in a chicken and he shot the chicken which I paid for the bullets.

0:11:58.140,0:12:03.440
He shot the chicken more than six times but the bullets did not enter.

0:12:03.440,0:12:09.680
He said that I had seen this, it had come to my turn.

0:12:09.680,0:12:15.640
I looked at him and asked why he wanted to pressurise me and whether he wanted to kill me.

0:12:15.640,0:12:19.940
He told me that he had fortified me and he needed to test it on me.

0:12:19.940,0:12:22.500
I told him if he had fortified himself, I would like to test it on him

0:12:22.500,0:12:32.560
but I would not allow him to test it on me as it was impossible.

0:12:32.560,0:12:45.060
He told me that since I was afraid, I had to call my mum before the test, in case I died.

0:12:45.060,0:12:48.700
He challenged me by telling me that I am a man.

0:12:48.700,0:12:52.720
I told him that if he had to test it on me, I didn’t want it anymore.

0:12:52.720,0:12:57.300
I said that since he had fortified me and I had paid, I would say thank you and I needed to go.

0:12:57.300,0:13:05.280
He gave me one chalk and one bangle I needed to put on.

0:13:05.280,0:13:09.240
He told me that when I travelled, every morning, I should do incantation

0:13:09.240,0:13:12.840
and use the chalk to draw anything or write me name

0:13:12.840,0:13:20.520
and speak out what I needed and it would come to pass.

0:13:20.520,0:13:25.500
I agreed and collected those stuffs.

0:13:25.500,0:13:29.040
I went back to my house.

0:13:29.040,0:13:35.140
My flight ticket would be for the following week.

0:13:35.140,0:13:38.560
I realised that I would not be able to carry those things he gave me in my flight.

0:13:38.560,0:13:45.620
I had to come back to him because it looked like drugs as it was white.

0:13:45.620,0:13:50.600
I asked myself, "How am I going to take it on-board?"

0:13:50.600,0:14:04.340
He said that he would pack it inside a soap bar and seal it back.

0:14:04.340,0:14:09.600
He did everything and gave it back to me.

0:14:09.600,0:14:14.760
I went to the airport and I was a little bit afraid if they noticed it

0:14:14.760,0:14:19.840
but after scanning me, they did not see anything.

0:14:19.840,0:14:23.060
I entered my flight. I travelled succesful.

0:14:23.060,0:14:28.640
In my mind, I thought I would bring millions of naira back to Nigeria.

0:14:28.640,0:14:35.640
As I had been fortified and I was already inside the plane, I was enjoying.

0:14:35.640,0:14:42.280
I started singing that I would come back to Nigeria in a bigger way.

0:14:42.280,0:14:45.560
I arrived in South Africa.

0:14:45.560,0:14:49.080
In the morning, I did that incantation because I didn’t want to waste time.

0:14:49.080,0:14:50.960
I needed money immediately.

0:14:50.960,0:14:56.680
Everything I told this man to do for me – I asked him to make me wealthy and strong -

0:14:56.680,0:15:05.180
