0:15:05.180,0:15:15.620
I stayed in South Africa for more than two years but I couldn’t boast of anything.

0:15:15.620,0:15:24.100
The residence permit – I didn’t have papers.

0:15:24.100,0:15:29.460
That really tormented me and even gave me sexual urge.

0:15:29.460,0:15:32.760
I didn’t like young woman.

0:15:32.760,0:15:46.660
In South Africa, I used to go out with old people who are above 50 years - that's my favourite.

0:15:46.660,0:15:52.420
My friends knew me.

0:15:52.420,0:15:58.880
If there were young girls, my friends would tell me, "This is not your 'food'. Your 'food' is old people."

0:15:58.880,0:16:00.480
OK.

0:16:00.480,0:16:03.580
