0:16:03.580,0:16:08.660
We want to take you back for a while; so people would know the reason why

0:16:08.660,0:16:13.560
only Jesus Christ is the way, the truth and the life, and there is no other way.

0:16:13.560,0:16:16.800
There is no hope from spiritualists or witch-doctors.

0:16:16.800,0:16:21.120
You said you went to the second witch-doctor and he gave you a stone with a red cloth to swallow.

0:16:21.120,0:16:25.100
Could you tell us exactly what happened to you instantly you swallowed the red cloth with a stone

0:16:25.100,0:16:28.220
