0:16:28.220,0:16:29.440
OK.

0:16:29.440,0:16:42.760
Immediately I knelt down, he gave me a red cloth that has a stone in it to swallow with water -

0:16:42.760,0:16:53.680
I felt something heavy entered me - it was as if more than 50 giants entered me.

0:16:53.680,0:16:59.900
Every night, I started seeing myself making love with old people in my dreams.

0:16:59.900,0:17:12.160
I started making love with old people in the dream before I travelled and did it in my real life.

0:17:12.160,0:17:18.180
