0:17:18.180,0:17:20.760
Sometimes, I would wound them or they would wound me.

0:17:20.760,0:17:27.200
Immediately I woke up, I would scream in the house.

0:17:27.200,0:17:33.600
Everybody would wake up and asked what was wrong with me but I didn't want to tell them.

0:17:33.600,0:17:40.420
So, instead of witch-doctors, native-doctors making you rich and more prosperous,

0:17:40.420,0:17:42.500
it was poverty and nightmares?

0:17:42.500,0:17:48.100
Yes, that was what they gave me but what I went there for was for him to make me rich.

0:17:48.100,0:17:50.640
He collected my money and gave me poverty.

0:17:50.640,0:17:54.100
OK, you said that in the dream you started seeing old women making love to you.

0:17:54.100,0:17:57.720
What happened to you in the physical world?

0:17:57.720,0:18:03.320
In the dream, I started seeing old women making love with me.

0:18:03.320,0:18:05.980
Immediately they finished making love with me,

0:18:05.980,0:18:14.900
I would find myself automatically wet when I woke up and I would be very weak

0:18:14.900,0:18:22.180
and that day would be a very bad day for me.

0:18:22.180,0:18:28.920
In the morning or afternoon I would be thinking of an old woman

0:18:28.920,0:18:33.040
because I didn’t do things with young women.

0:18:33.040,0:18:36.760
After that, I travelled with it.

0:18:36.760,0:18:43.460
Everything that happened to me in the dream while I was still in Nigeria, I started doing it in South Africa.

0:18:43.460,0:18:49.960
I started sleeping with old women of 50-60 years – that was my favourite in South Africa.

0:18:49.960,0:18:54.120
Everything I put my hand on there was not working.

0:18:54.120,0:19:02.580
After seeing that nothing was working for me in South Africa, I applied for a job.

0:19:02.580,0:19:09.340
They would do interview on phone and after the interview, they would be impressed

0:19:09.340,0:19:12.360
and ask me to come to see me physically.

0:19:12.360,0:19:16.260
Immediately I appeared physically, that job would not be given to me.

0:19:16.260,0:19:18.580
I would not get that job again.

0:19:18.580,0:19:24.680
This happened to me once, twice, thrice – I knew the cause.

0:19:24.680,0:19:28.380
I called my friend that introduced me to that native doctor.

0:19:28.380,0:19:43.520
I asked him to remind me the reason we went to the native doctor because I forgot it.

0:19:43.520,0:19:49.240
He said that we went there for me to be rich and he was expecting me to send him money.

0:19:49.240,0:19:51.920
I told him, “You are very stupid.

0:19:51.920,0:20:01.080
Do you know that right now, I am begging to eat, talkless of sending you money?

0:20:01.080,0:20:08.620
Starting from today, deceive me no more!”

0:20:08.620,0:20:12.180
When I was there, I couldn’t boast of anything.

0:20:12.180,0:20:19.740
It was my mum I would disturb to send me money.

0:20:19.740,0:20:29.840
Almost every month, the money I used to pay my house rent in South Africa was from my mum.

0:20:29.840,0:20:39.200
I was in South Africa frustrated and tired – I didn’t know what to do anymore.

0:20:39.200,0:20:45.860
I prepared my passport and travelled to Israel.

0:20:45.860,0:20:58.940
When I was in Israel, God blessed me – I stared working in a hotel as a receptionist.

0:20:58.940,0:21:05.380
I could see that my life was changing.

0:21:05.380,0:21:09.280
I sent my first salary to my mum.

0:21:09.280,0:21:11.820
She was very happy.

0:21:11.820,0:21:15.680
She said that after many years, she just received my money.

0:21:15.680,0:21:18.500
I said, “Mummy, don’t worry. The bigger one is coming”.

0:21:18.500,0:21:23.860
Then, I was not is South Africa anymore where I should sleep with an old woman before I could eat.

0:21:23.860,0:21:28.080
I didn’t tell her about it.

0:21:28.080,0:21:35.300
While I was there, my papers got expired.

0:21:35.300,0:21:40.640
When I tried to renew my papers, they said that my papers was fake.

0:21:40.640,0:21:50.980
I asked them how I could have entered Israel with fake papers and even got a job with it.

0:21:50.980,0:21:58.660
They told me that the papers was fake and they could not renew it.

0:21:58.660,0:22:08.660
They did not want to arrest me because of my lawyer who was a strong woman.

0:22:08.660,0:22:10.900
I knew what was happening to me.

0:22:10.900,0:22:14.900
Immediately they told me that, I remembered what I did in Nigeria.

0:22:14.900,0:22:17.460
I knew that was the same thing that was following me.

0:22:17.460,0:22:27.560
I decided to come back to Nigeria to clear myself from darkness and fix my papers.

0:22:27.560,0:22:36.760
I came back to Nigeria to renew my papers which they called fake.

0:22:36.760,0:22:41.080
There was no way I could travel back.

0:22:41.080,0:22:43.860
I tried everything to go back but there was no way.

0:22:43.860,0:22:50.440
I called the company I worked for and told them that everything was OK.

0:22:50.440,0:22:54.740
They sent me an invitation letter to come back but there was no way.

0:22:54.740,0:23:03.940
That was what I was going through before I discovered Emmanuel TV.

0:23:03.940,0:23:14.100
I was in my house, frustrated, tired and angry with my life; I didn’t know what to do.

0:23:14.100,0:23:28.820
I turned on my TV to watch an action movie but it was not clear.

0:23:28.820,0:23:35.680
I was changing channels before I saw Emmanuel TV.

0:23:35.680,0:23:39.940
I saw Prophet T.B. Joshua praying.

0:23:39.940,0:23:50.340
I was sitting down alone.

0:23:50.340,0:23:54.280
I started watching the prophet praying.

0:23:54.280,0:24:02.820
I was thinking in my heart, he would not ask me to pay 100,000 or 50,000.

0:24:02.820,0:24:07.120
Then, I decided to come and see.

0:24:07.120,0:24:11.880
If he would also ask for money, I would run away.

0:24:11.880,0:24:22.980
When I stepped my feet in the arena of liberty, I began seeing a lot of changes.

0:24:22.980,0:24:30.080
The SCOAN Sunday Service

0:24:30.080,0:24:34.560
I began seeing a lot of changes.

0:24:34.560,0:24:38.200
When the choir was singing, I could feel goose-bumps.

0:24:38.200,0:24:41.880
I could feel the real presence of God.

0:24:41.880,0:24:47.460
Everything that happened to me all these while, I began to view it.

0:24:47.460,0:24:54.440
I believed everything I needed and where I would get my deliverance was here.

0:24:54.440,0:25:00.680
I was wondering how could the prophet locate me where there were millions of people here.

0:25:00.680,0:25:03.480
It seemed to be impossible.

0:25:03.480,0:25:06.640
I decided to pray.

0:25:06.640,0:25:11.960
I believe as I pray, my problem would be solved.

0:25:11.960,0:25:17.600
Another voice was telling me that I was wasting my time as I was also praying before.

0:25:17.600,0:25:20.540
The voice asked me how this one would make a difference.

0:25:20.540,0:25:23.280
I began to reason with the voice.

0:25:23.280,0:25:29.160
I went outside and the irritation and anger came upon me again.

0:25:29.160,0:25:34.280
I went outside and bought a bottle of water and came inside again.

0:25:34.280,0:25:37.560
I was tired to stay there.

0:25:37.560,0:25:42.800
Immediately the prophet came in, I rushed back to my seat.

0:25:42.800,0:25:46.260
Prophet T.B. Joshua was touching people.

0:25:46.260,0:25:51.460
Behold, he went straight to my line.

0:25:51.460,0:25:55.500
I was among the people he touched.

0:25:55.500,0:26:02.200
What a wonderful God!

0:26:02.200,0:26:10.200
That is not enough for Jesus Christ - put you hands together beautifully for the miracle working God!

0:26:10.200,0:26:15.560
It is a clear proof that weeping may endure for a night but the joy comes in the morning.

0:26:15.560,0:26:19.260
Indeed, he has suffered a lot, been to several places in search of a solution

0:26:19.260,0:26:26.160
but when it was God's time to manifest His deliverance in his life, it happened just like that.

0:26:26.160,0:26:30.980
Tell us; the moment the man of God laid hand on you - how did you feel inside you that brought about your deliverance?

0:26:30.980,0:26:35.940
Immediately Prophet T.B. Joshua laid his hand on me,

0:26:35.940,0:26:45.820
that 50 giants that entered me in the shrine where they collected my money - everything jumped out of me.

0:26:45.820,0:26:52.040
I was so free and became light.

0:26:52.040,0:26:54.820
I felt something came out of me.

0:26:54.820,0:26:57.800
The time those giants jumped inside me, I could feel it.

0:26:57.800,0:27:04.320
When they jumped out, I could feel it again.

0:27:04.320,0:27:11.560
That is not enough for Jesus Christ; put your hands together beautifully for the miracle working God.

0:27:11.560,0:27:13.120
You heard it all.

0:27:13.120,0:27:19.820
Right in the shrine he was possessed by 50 giants, and he knew they entered his life.

0:27:19.820,0:27:24.160
He said, that here, in the arena of liberty, when the man of God laid hand upon him;

0:27:24.160,0:27:26.080
the moment the giants left him, he also knew about it.

0:27:26.080,0:27:32.020
Let's clap for wonderful Jesus Christ once again.

0:27:32.020,0:27:37.780
Can you tell us; since you have been delivered - what are the changes you have seen in your life?

0:27:37.780,0:27:43.000
Since I have been delivered, I have no more urge for old women.

0:27:43.000,0:27:46.800
When they chat with me, I will be seriously irritated.

0:27:46.800,0:27:53.400
They know something is wrong because they don’t know that I am a new creation.

0:27:53.400,0:27:54.500
I am very free.

0:27:54.500,0:27:57.620
I don’t want to go back to my old life.

0:27:57.620,0:27:58.660
Amen.

0:27:58.660,0:28:02.200
What word of advice do you have for all who are listening to you?

0:28:02.200,0:28:11.060
The word of advice I have for young people is that you cannot go faster than your shadow.

0:28:11.060,0:28:13.680
Wait upon the Lord.

0:28:13.680,0:28:17.740
I ran faster than my shadow; I ran to get everything immediately

0:28:17.740,0:28:24.960
but I entered where they were destroying me slowly.

0:28:24.960,0:28:28.300
I thought I would be rich.

0:28:28.300,0:28:30.160
To God be the glory.

